"Individual support services" includes:
Identification services;
Training and support for self-advocacy;
Therapeutic services;
Individual and family counseling;
Medical equipment purchase, rental, and repair;
Crisis intervention and follow-up;
Attendant care;
Respite services;
Barrier removal;
Transportation assistance;
Community integration services;
Employment related services; and
Other services to maximize independence, productivity, and integration within the community.
